name: sa4_p41b_industry_of_employment_by_age_by_sex_census_2016
title: SA4-P41b Industry of Employment by Age by Sex-Census 2016

legal.licenceType: Creative Commons Attribution 2.5 Australia (CC BY 2.5 AU)

abstract:
SA4 based data for Industry of Employment by Age by Sex, in Place of Enumeration Profile (PEP), 2016 Census. Count of employed persons aged 15 years and over (excludes overseas visitors). P41 is broken up into four sections (P41a - P41d), this section contains 'Males Total Age 15-19 years' - 'Females Other services Total'. The data is by SA4 2016 boundaries. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
Note: There are small random adjustments made to all cell values to protect the confidentiality of data. These adjustments may cause the sum of rows or columns to differ by small amounts from table totals.
For more information visit the data source: http://www.abs.gov.au/census.
